-- Egypt's Heliopolis Housing July-March profit up 37 pct 
-- 
-- Tue Apr 15, 2014 05:13AM EDT
-- None



CAIRO, April 15 (Reuters) - Egypt's Heliopolis Company for Housing and Construction <HELI.CA> rpeorted post-tax profit up 37 percent to 122.5 million Egyptian pounds ($18 million) in the nine months to March 31, boosted by stronger sales.

Sales revenue rose 17 percent year on year to 245.12 million pounds, the company said in a statement to the stock exchange.